metadata.description: A Rug Radio Membership Pass is step one in getting you set up as an owner in the Rug ecosystem. You will use this Membership Pass as a mint pass to our genesis drop, however, it is more than a mint pass. Your Membership Pass will be the key to how you connect to and derive value from the Rug Radio  ecosystem. You can think of it as an all-access pass to everything Rug Radio. We highly recommend you hold onto your Membership Pass tight! We have big plans for you!
metadata.name: Rug Radio Membership Pass
